    Orignal source file as obtained from the ASPIS project cluster on Google Drive

    data_source.Rd

    A dataset containing information (ids) on 790 compounds, collected from three Horizon 2020 projects (RISK-HUNT3R, ONTOX and PrecisionTox), organized under an umbrella organization called ASPIS. See ASPIS for more details.

    Usage

    data_source

    Format

    A data frame with 790 rows and 12 variables:

    Compound Name

    The generic name of the compound

    IUPAC

    Standardized IUPAC chemical name

    Inchi

    The inchi of the compound

    SMILES

    The SMILES string to conceptualize the molecular structure

    CAS number

    The number according the CAS registry

    DTXSID

    EPA CompTox Dashboard compound id

    Project ID (RISK-HUNT3R)

    Internal id for RISK-HUNT3R project

    Project ID (ONTOX)

    Internal id for ONTOX project

    Project ID (PrecisionTox)

    Internal id for PrecisionTox project

    Used in RISK-HUNT3R

    Whether the compound is used in RISK-HUNT3R

    Used in ONTOX

    Whether the compound is used in ONTOX

    Used in PrecisionTox

    Whether the compound is used in PrecisionTox

    Source

    Google Drive
